{"tid":1039993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"見到當日你飛嘅佢依家同另一半過得幸福快樂","createTime":"2019-02-27T20:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T14:57:32.000Z","uid":113981,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ded6edf776217483f975479d9286c76be241145","tid":1039993,"uid":113981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:10:08.000Z","msg":"想對天下所有賤男講：<br />\n當初你狠狠地飛條女個陣<br />\n佢死求爛求 你就覺得甩難 <br />\n到左今日<br />\n你唔係覺得自己會一直高高在上 <br />\n仲以為佢無左你會死啊嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢只會感激當日你放佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見一直以來好多post都話忘記唔到ex <br />\n唔捨得好想挽留 甚至可以做到好無尊嚴<br />\n我想以過來人身分同大家講<br />\n其實move on 離開佢先係對自己最好 人生流流長 總會遇到一個真正合適你 相處舒服 互相珍惜愛護嘅人<br />\n而好明顯對方對你造成所有嘅傷害證明左佢唔係對的人<br />\n到你遇到依個人 你會感謝前任嘅傷害 感激自己離開<br />\n然後更珍惜段感情得到真正嘅幸福<br />\n<br />\n若然未遇到 不過時晨未到<br />\n抹乾眼涙 好好增值自己去迎接依個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476d4244e4bbe33fecf4883d611584a6ae99596b","tid":1039993,"uid":189128,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:40:04.000Z","msg":"講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好認同你講既嘢<br />\n唔好覺得同賤男一齊係自己既恩典咁<br />\n分開左係甩難"},{"pid":"cdf2eb213150858fb35540c7cec3e6fd3c9a0e27","tid":1039993,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁如果係大家喊哂口話性格不合，和平分手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9633f9f8052feb76e6ca2b6901b9699c6378eb","tid":1039993,"uid":113981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cdf2eb213150858fb35540c7cec3e6fd3c9a0e27","tid":1039993,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁如果係大家喊哂口話性格不合，